{
  "stem": "19982.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in Wroclaw, we knew that we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was-- and at this time, I was already, like, going with my husband.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bernard, Bernard Muschel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and we were thinking how-- I really wanted to go very much to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I felt that this would be my place from now on, since I didn't have anybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For me, it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Every single night, I was daydreaming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was crying, putting myself to sleep with the hope-- I was always saying, maybe my mother-- maybe she's sick.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe she's gonna-- maybe she have amnesia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe she's going to come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father, I knew, will not because they told me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was killed the first in the city because he refused to go to Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He knew the ramification for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he really didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, I'm not going to work with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was the first one to be killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So him, I knew he was killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But my mother, I knew that they took her to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I always had a-- because she went with my cousins, which cousin-- which one survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so I figured maybe, maybe she's someplace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this was my daydream and night dream.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I always put myself to sleep with the hope [SOBBING] I'm sure they're going to find me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm sure she's sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm sure something-- I'm sure she's going to find me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then, when we were in Wroclaw, we were thinking how-- my uncle was thinking how to get out from, from Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So now, before-- oh yes, before-- I wanted to go home back to my town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And a cousin of mine, which was-- it was very difficult to travel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You couldn't travel.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
